description:
Open for recipe 

Saucy and flavorful, these classic vegan Philly cheesesteak sandwiches combine high-protein vegan seitan steak strips with sauteed portobello mushrooms and bell peppers in a hefty hoagie roll. If youre hankering for something hot and substantial that you can whip together in a hurry, this is it! Cheesy, meaty, gooey deliciousness! 

Vegan Philly Cheesesteak
2 bell peppers
2 portobello mushrooms
1 onion
1 tsp extra virgin olive oil
2 tbsp nutritional yeast flakes
 tsp smoked paprika
Salt and pepper to taste
4 seitan strips
1 small jalapeno pepper (optional)
2-3 tbsp vegan barbecue sauce (optional)
 c shredded vegan cheese
Vegan cheese slices

Vegan, dairy free. To make it gluten free, replace seitan slices with GF vegan meat alternative and substitute GF buns for hoagie rolls.
